    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I bet you tested this on a dedicated or MP server.  This happens because all the settings except the ones you mention operate via an order.  The checkbox is \"checked\" from the mouse-down state, then goes unchecked while the order is in flight, then rechecks once it is finally parsed.\n\nThis can be fixed by predicting the final state, like we do for pausing.\n"
